Use Jira as Prototype
EPIC
* User Story 
 - user story
 - user story description
 - priority
 - assignee
 - sprint
 - * Task
    --  task id,
    --  task description

-- * Test Case
  -- Test Script contains steps (Step1: Step 2 etc)
  -- Test Script Status (Open |Complete | In Progress)
  -- Test Script Results ( attach results or evidence)

Each User Story ---->  Multiple Tasks
                ---->  Multiple Test Cases

Tracebility -- US1 --> TC1, TC2, TC3 ....--
